I am not going to hurt anyone.

6
00:00:31,434 --> 00:00:32,734
You have no free will.

7
00:00:32,767 --> 00:00:36,601
And you're destined to
become what you really are.

8
00:00:36,634 --> 00:00:37,767
Doomsday.

9
