14
00:01:12,467 --> 00:01:14,267
Great! Thank you!

15
00:01:14,300 --> 00:01:16,567
Nice to be back!

16
00:01:16,601 --> 00:01:18,067
Lois!

17
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:19,734
Are you kidding me?!

18
00:01:19,767 --> 00:01:21,234
<i>Now you show up?</i>

19
00:01:21,267 --> 00:01:23,167
The one time i actually depend on you,

20
