me up from the airport.

21
00:01:25,534 --> 00:01:27,501
I'm really sorry.

22
00:01:27,534 --> 00:01:28,868
Sorry?!

23
00:01:28,901 --> 00:01:32,100
Sorry doesn't buy back the
last three hours i spent ...

24
00:01:32,133 --> 00:01:36,634
standing in a downpour...

25
00:01:37,901 --> 00:01:39,734
...watching cheesy curbside reunions.

26
00:01:39,767 --> 00:01:40,868
I can explain.

27
00:01:40,901 --> 00:01:42,767
You e-mailed last night
to say you'd be there.

28
00:01:42,801 --> 00:01:45,501
What, do i need to tie a string
around your finger myself?

29
00:01:45,534 --> 00:01:47,000
But i got held up a-at work.

30
00:01:47,033 --> 00:01:48,501
I finished one thing, lois,

31
00:01:48,534 --> 00:01:50,200
and something else would come up.

32
