about little orphan alien.

70
00:03:50,601 --> 00:03:53,834
We've gone through this
before. I'll stop you.

71
00:03:53,868 --> 00:03:55,300
Not this time.

72
00:03:55,334 --> 00:03:58,701
You'll make a great headline, kent.

