Jimmy's being transferred to met gen,

78
00:05:13,933 --> 00:05:16,734
and i don't think he's
into a chick flick.

79
00:05:16,768 --> 00:05:18,701
You okay?

80
00:05:18,734 --> 00:05:20,701
Linda lake is back.

81
00:05:20,734 --> 00:05:22,267
What?

82
