244
00:15:08,268 --> 00:15:10,201
It's not fair to jimmy.

245
00:15:10,234 --> 00:15:12,567
I'm sorry, but we can't run a hospital

246
00:15:12,600 --> 00:15:15,034
when everybody's clamoring for pictures.

247
00:15:15,067 --> 00:15:16,533
Of a guy in a neck brace?

248
00:15:16,567 --> 00:15:20,634
A guy in a neck brace married
to the alien's best friend.

249
00:15:33,167 --> 00:15:35,433
Davis.

250
00:15:35,467 --> 00:15:37,101
When did you get back?

251
00:15:37,134 --> 00:15:38,567
Chloe. Hey.

252
00:15:38,600 --> 00:15:41,234
Uh, just a few days ago.

253
00:15:43,067 --> 00:15:45,167
I think we should talk
about what happened.

254
00:15:47,634 --> 00:15:48,767
You remember?

255
00:15:48,800 --> 00:15:51,134
Well, it's kind of hard to forget.

256
00:15:51,167 --> 00:15:53,067
I mean...

257
00:15:53,101 --> 00:15:54,567
you kissed me.

258
00:15:56,800 --> 00:15:58,234
Right, yeah.

259
00:15:58,268 --> 00:15:59,234
Uh...

260
00:15:59,268 --> 00:16:00,368
yeah, i'm assuming

261
00:16:00,400 --> 00:16:02,700
that that's what all the
phone calls were about.

262
00:16:02,734 --> 00:16:05,234
I sort of deleted the
messages without listening.

263
00:16:05,268 --> 00:16:07,268
Yeah, well, you didn't miss much.

